==External links== * [http://weblog.ceicher.com/archives/2006/12/ibm_system360_green_card.html IBM/360 Green card image] by Charles Eicher * [http://planetmvs.com/greencard/index.html Green, yellow and other cards] by Dave Alcock * [http://weblog.ceicher.com/archives/IBM360greencard.pdf Complete reference card] in PDF format. * [http://proc.isecon.org/2007/3743/ISECON.2007.Waguespack.pdf A "green card" for OOP] by Leslie J. Waguespack, Jr., Ph.D. from 2007
